{"tid":1576580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"穆迪下調港鐵(00066.HK)及九廣鐵路評級展望至「負面」","createTime":"2019-09-17T10:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T10:39:48.000Z","uid":28114,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"21eac16fa20c4f278218532b92ae5895923b0446","tid":1576580,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:02:28.000Z","msg":"評級機構穆迪下調港鐵(<a href=\"http://00066.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00066.HK&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=1e65f1ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00066.HK</a>)  -0.600 (-1.282%)    沽空 $4.72千萬; 比率 22.602%   及九廣鐵路評級展望，由「穩定」轉為「負面」，以依隨把香港評級展望由「穩定」轉為「負面」的決定。<br />\n<br />\n穆迪指，港鐵(<a href=\"http://00066.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00066.HK&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=1e65f1ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00066.HK</a>)  -0.600 (-1.282%)    沽空 $4.72千萬; 比率 22.602%   及九廣鐵路均為政府相關債券發行人，評級及展望與香港政府緊密相連。因此下調香港評級展望對兩者均產生負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵(<a href=\"http://00066.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00066.HK&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=1e65f1ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00066.HK</a>)  -0.600 (-1.282%)    沽空 $4.72千萬; 比率 22.602%   及九廣鐵路的目前信貸評級為「Aa2」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.966010/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.966010%2F2&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=cecd39cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.966010/2</a>"},{"pid":"2c6dc211ecbfd99a7d2190898643449f75883feb","tid":1576580,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img sr